Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.32,0:00:33.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.04,0:00:39.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道本小姐是常盘台中学的婚后光子么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.59,0:02:46.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.51,0:02:48.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院之苑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:49.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你这么说啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.58,0:02:53.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只不过是女校聚在一起的镇子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.50,0:02:57.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那些聚起来的学校不普通了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.89,0:03:02.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了常盘台中学之外  其它也都是些出名的大小姐学校哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.55,0:03:04.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个的确没错…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:08.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天是因为被白井同学招待了才能进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:14.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然的话  像我们这样的平民是一辈子都无缘的地方哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.71,0:03:17.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真自卑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.40,0:03:20.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说初春你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.70,0:03:22.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  这个是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.55,0:03:29.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛  佐天同学其实已经把今天要去的蛋糕店查过了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.21,0:03:32.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是「Pasticceria Manicagni」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:35.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使用精选的材料  再加以地道的意大利配方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.26,0:03:40.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烘烤出来的芝士蛋糕正可谓艺术品啊  上面不也写着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.02,0:03:42.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个之前开始一直都想吃一次看看
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.09,0:03:45.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是在日本只在学院之苑里面才有店面
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:48.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学意外地喜欢追潮流呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.27,0:03:52.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一站是  学院之苑站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.02,0:03:54.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院之苑站
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  巴士比预计时间早到了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.91,0:04:04.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:07.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,3  2  1
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.12,0:04:13.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然这座城市的天气预报很准确呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.82,0:04:15.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说是预报
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.12,0:04:20.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确地说是通过对未来的演算来解读和确定未来的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:25.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得偶尔失误一下也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:28.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个  快点走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.80,0:04:38.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是被常盘台中学一年级的白井黑子所邀请的初春饰利和
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.62,0:04:39.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天泪子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.93,0:04:43.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  可以放行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.31,0:05:11.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是多么惹人怜爱的城镇啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.33,0:05:13.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从人行道到交通灯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.22,0:05:15.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有设计都跟外面不同
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.99,0:05:17.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都很讲究呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,简直就像来到了异国一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.10,0:05:23.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:31.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…总觉得我们好像被人看着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:32.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是因为这副打扮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:39.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概是外面的学生在这里比较少见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.84,0:05:41.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕  已经到时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.68,0:05:47.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.50,0:05:49.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来  走快点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她们两个真晚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.29,0:05:58.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,集合是在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.45,0:06:03.89,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  想看看我们学校所以才特意在校门外等的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.01,0:06:07.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  让姐姐大人等她们真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.99,0:06:08.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.85,0:06:13.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:14.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.15,0:06:16.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在水洼上稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.57,0:06:25.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便你突然说想换衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.21,0:06:28.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也只能准备到这些了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.28,0:06:30.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  已经足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.43,0:06:34.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.03,0:06:36.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚刚好…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.32,0:06:39.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裙子有点短  凉飕飕的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.67,0:06:42.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有佐天同学一个真不公平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.56,0:06:46.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  跟我的制服交换吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.35,0:06:47.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这么做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.39,0:06:48.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.36,0:06:50.16,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太小了不行的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.59,0:06:52.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  我也去踩水洼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.44,0:06:53.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.76,0:06:55.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微一下就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.67,0:07:01.39,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄脏的制服已经拿去洗了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.75,0:07:02.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回来的时候记得拿哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.46,0:07:07.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果觉得麻烦的话能够直接送到你的宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.08,0:07:09.46,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是常盘台
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:13.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是女仆吗  果然是女仆去做的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.33,0:07:14.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷静点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.30,0:07:21.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,草莓派…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.63,0:07:25.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不  Monte Bianco看起来也很好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.51,0:07:29.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个巧克力塔也无法释手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.17,0:07:31.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么值得烦恼么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:35.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我已经决定要芝士蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.31,0:07:38.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不快点的话就到晚上了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.17,0:07:41.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:45.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.75,0:07:47.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.85,0:07:51.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.26,0:07:53.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又被召集了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:54.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.34,0:07:57.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有比这个时机更糟糕了的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.69,0:08:01.86,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春的那份由我们带回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.98,0:08:03.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.02,0:08:06.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们快走吧初春
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.60,0:08:07.17,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:10.22,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还真忙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.89,0:08:12.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我们先…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:16.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…我稍微去一下洗手间
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.83,0:08:25.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  难得的星期六的休假日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:26.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.95,0:08:27.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.31,0:08:30.36,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别刚刚到就抱怨
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.67,0:08:32.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  固法前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.78,0:08:35.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么叫我们来是什么理由呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:38.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从昨天放学后到晚上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.49,0:08:43.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了专门针对常盘台的袭击事件  有六人受到了袭击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.40,0:08:49.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且全都在学院之苑里发生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.67,0:09:01.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台中学里面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有强能力者以上的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:03.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(280,328)\fs18}Level 3
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.48,0:09:08.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以其为袭击目标  并轻而易举地将其打倒的人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.47,0:09:10.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是相当强的能力者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.21,0:09:13.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能性很高呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.30,0:09:16.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是能力还没弄清
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.53,0:09:17.91,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害者全部都是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.98,0:09:28.25,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被电枪所击晕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.26,0:09:33.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么失去意识的受害者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽说有照片…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:38.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是很惨不忍睹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.71,0:09:42.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要看的话  请做好觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:50.23,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,红茶都凉了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,志愿参加了风纪委员早就有这种觉悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.47,0:09:55.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(289,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:57.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.10,0:09:59.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.12,0:10:01.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.92,0:10:09.50,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:14.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.60,0:10:16.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.80,0:10:27.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常盘台猎人？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.69,0:10:30.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此  因为穿了我们的制服
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.92,0:10:32.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,情况怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.96,0:10:35.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身体上好像没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.64,0:10:38.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时先让她躺下就没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:39.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嫌犯有头绪了么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.14,0:10:47.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还没有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.90,0:10:50.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起来是个稍微有点麻烦的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:51.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说的麻烦是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.78,0:10:54.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.98,0:11:00.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的  我谁都没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:05.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…但是  从监视摄像头的录像来看…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:06.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.20,0:11:09.61,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的没看见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.98,0:11:14.34,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受害者看不见的嫌犯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.80,0:11:19.06,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最初怀疑的是光学操纵系的能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.47,0:11:24.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够完全隐身的能力者在学园都市有47名
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.29,0:11:28.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是所有的人都有不在场证明
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.66,0:11:31.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,况且  不是被监视摄像头照到了么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.97,0:11:34.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这应该不像光学操纵系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.40,0:11:36.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.90,0:11:38.88,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  鸽子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.82,0:11:41.82,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白井同学没看见么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:44.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那点事情没发觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.86,0:11:46.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.48,0:11:51.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春同学  有点事想查一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.83,0:11:55.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能力名是「虚假检验」
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.91,0:11:57.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(360,328)\fs18}Dummy Check
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.91,0:12:02.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是直接阻碍人对眼中的对象的认知的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.86,0:12:04.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该能力的使用者只有一人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.21,0:12:08.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关所中学二年级的重福省帆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:10.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这个人是异能力者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(370,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.90,0:12:19.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实验数据是这样表明的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.09,0:12:17.55,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的能力并不足以将自己的存在感完全抹消
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.47,0:12:23.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为能有所突破了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.76,0:12:31.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:32.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.31,0:12:33.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.80,0:12:48.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎怎怎怎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.93,0:12:51.10,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  请保持镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.68,0:12:54.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想必很受打击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.87,0:12:59.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少也得有这个长度的刘海才能藏得住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.46,0:13:00.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刘海？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.15,0:13:03.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就…就是她
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.64,0:13:06.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到犯人了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:07.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.48,0:13:09.26,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.82,0:13:14.66,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在镜子中确实映出了她的容貌
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.60,0:13:20.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,镜子…监视器…原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.68,0:13:25.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的能力的作用对象仅局限于直接用肉眼观察
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:31.03,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眉毛的仇恨  岂能忍气吞声
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.62,0:13:32.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧  初春
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:34.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:49.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.46,0:13:53.85,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不这么做的话  这里的电脑终端是无法跟上处理速度的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.21,0:14:00.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  学院之苑并非归177支部所管辖  不要紧吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:03.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得到上面的批准了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.43,0:14:06.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  初春  放手去干吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.10,0:14:07.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.56,0:14:17.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学院之苑的监视器共2458台
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.91,0:14:19.08,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经全部连接上了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:22.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等着吧  刘海女
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.42,0:14:26.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我怎么把你给揪出来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.24,0:14:29.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可别忘了约好的蛋糕哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.42,0:14:31.93,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三个也好四个也罢  保证让你吃个够
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.04,0:14:32.74,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.40,0:14:34.49,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.95,0:14:35.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.69,0:14:37.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  没关系的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.09,0:14:40.12,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是指蛋糕啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.16,0:14:45.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  将区域E到H  以及J和N忽略掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.29,0:14:46.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:52.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些地方距离常盘台最远
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:55.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以鲜有本校学生出没
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:59.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那人流量大的地方也暂时排除
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:01.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.08,0:15:03.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以犯人的服装
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.18,0:15:05.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是出现在学院之苑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.18,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得会很引人注目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.81,0:15:09.73,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.04,0:15:13.60,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是指犯人持续使用能力以避人耳目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.82,0:15:14.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.05,0:15:18.77,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  能力是无法永远持续使用的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:22.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说她躲在没人耳目的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.79,0:15:24.62,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正确
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.18,0:15:26.72,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.99,0:15:49.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.09,0:15:53.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那可爱的眉毛的帐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.92,0:15:56.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可一分也别想赖掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.85,0:16:00.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的消失了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.41,0:16:03.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在可不是佩服的时候  快去追啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.24,0:16:05.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.58,0:16:09.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.44,0:16:11.32,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:13.90,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好像被什么撞到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:15.83,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.53,0:16:17.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.30,0:16:26.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这附近
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风纪委员  乖乖地束手就擒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.24,0:16:36.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(255,328)\fs18}Judgment
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.19,0:16:41.45,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然没那么老实呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.20,0:16:44.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  麻烦你带路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:45.76,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.57,0:16:49.38,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了巷子左拐  然后走三号街
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.58,0:16:50.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,了解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.55,0:16:51.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.41,0:16:52.01,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:55.99,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:16:59.97,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.00,0:17:01.69,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏就…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.66,0:17:32.58,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到此为止了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  为什么虚假检验会不起作用
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.93,0:17:37.30,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(338,328)\fs18}Dummy Check
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.98,0:17:39.75,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你觉得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:44.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是因为这样常盘台的家伙才…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:01.24,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遗憾  我可是不吃这一套的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.78,0:18:04.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.41,0:18:15.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经手下留情了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:20.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  麻烦你向警备员汇报一下犯人已经抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:20.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(275,328)\fs18}Anti-Skill
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:21.95,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.08,0:18:22.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.65,0:18:29.37,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:39.52,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的眉毛画成怎么样才好呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:45.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:47.47,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.71,0:18:48.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.43,0:18:51.05,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么  我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.33,0:18:55.40,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想笑就笑个够吧  就像那个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.63,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.15,0:19:06.65,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天  我沐浴在和煦的阳光之中
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.87,0:19:12.19,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天真地认为  幸福的时光会永远延续下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.29,0:19:13.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.17,0:19:22.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天毫无预兆地消逝了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.52,0:19:26.79,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么  你就那么喜欢常盘台的大小姐吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.21,0:19:28.57,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不是那样的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.69,0:19:29.80,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.24,0:19:32.11,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为  你的眉毛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.10,0:19:35.29,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.03,0:19:42.13,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那个将我抛弃不顾的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.51,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨那个夺我所爱的常盘台的女人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.92,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且  更有甚者
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.58,0:19:51.81,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我恨这世上所有的眉毛
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.36,0:19:55.98,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我才想把大家的眉毛都涂成奇形怪状的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.10,0:19:57.09,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.37,0:20:00.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我从中途开始就一头雾水了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.42,0:20:06.21,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  想笑就笑啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.05,0:20:09.07,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.72,0:20:12.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是那么怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.34,0:20:16.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就好像是…那个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:19.94,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了  就是恰如其分的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.41,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是挺喜欢的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.58,0:20:29.14,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是罪孽深重的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:48.20,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问  我可以给你写信么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:51.27,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.06,0:21:09.35,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来她的隐身可谓天衣无缝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  她明明只是个异能力者的说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.10,0:21:13.53,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(390,328)\fs18}Level 2
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.67,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不合常理啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.24,0:21:18.56,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会不会是资料有误
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.68,0:21:21.04,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.49,0:21:28.31,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.85,0:21:31.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  其他受害者也是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.11,0:21:36.78,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那似乎是由第十学区开发的特殊墨水
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:40.15,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说在一周内是绝对无法消除的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.48,0:21:47.00,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  需要再给你准备一顶帽子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.68,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那个眉毛女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.15,0:21:53.64,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早知道就涂她个一头一脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.77,0:21:55.71,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐天同学  请保持镇定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.48,0:21:59.44,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么办才好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.49,0:23:32.42,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初春  你知道凉鞋婆婆吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.53,0:23:33.59,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凉…凉鞋婆婆？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.71,0:23:34.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说老婆婆会穿着凉鞋追上来
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.82,0:23:36.48,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时速超过100KM呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.61,0:23:36.87,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:37.84,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还一丝不挂
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.93,0:23:38.70,DefaultCN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好恶心

